        <br><strong>type</strong> <code>em (recommended), px</code>
    </li>
    <li>
        <code>$type-line-height-heading</code> defines header line heights
        <br><strong>default</strong> <code>1.4</code>
        <br><strong>type</strong> <code>em (recommended), px</code>
    </li>
</ul>

